Chapter 1

The sun was setting over the savannah, casting an orange glow across the grassy plains. A majestic lion stood atop a rocky outcrop, his golden mane blowing in the gentle breeze. His name was Simba, and he was the king of the pride.

Simba had been ruling over his pride for several years now, and he had seen many challenges in his time as the leader. But tonight, as he gazed out over the vast expanse of his kingdom, he felt a sense of unease that he couldn't quite shake.

Something was stirring in the savannah, and Simba knew that it was only a matter of time before he would have to face it head-on.


